data.title: Poway Dog Trainer
data.meta_description: Golan Dogs Is Owned and Led By a Veteran Special Warfare Canine Trainer. Based In Poway, With Over 17 Years Of Experience. Professional Dog Training, Behavior Modification, Board and Train, Obedience, Puppy Training, Private Lessons and More. Our Expertise Gives Us a Unique Set Of Skills Unmatched By Others.
data.text:
Puppy training your dog is undoubtedly the best decision you can take for both of you.

During the first year of your puppy's life you have a monumental opportunity and part in teaching the right skills your dog needs to be a good listener and follower. The opportunity to shape your puppy to be a well mannered, well adjusted and balanced dog that thrives is a golden one.

​

​

Learn more...

Start doing it right! Be the Leader!

Learn it best through 1-on-1 private sessions with us.

1-on-1 Private Lessons will give you crucial and indispensable tools, skills and education to maintain positive behavior and long term success. You will learn how to correct behavioral issues in advance and stop them from reoccurring or becoming a real problem. Address behavior issues and teach commands and obedience.

Learn more...

Give yourself a "Boost" in training. We will do the hard work, you get them back smarter.

Choose between 'Day Training' or 'Full Immersion'. Your dog spends his/her day with us going through 1-on-1 training sessions. Customized program to meet your needs and the needs of your dog. They get to socialize with dog members from my pack and utilize pack mentality for better dog obedience.

Learn more...
